// There should be no space between declare keyword and opening parenthesis.
'Expected no space between declare keyword and opening parenthesis in a declare statement'
// There should be no space between open parenthesis and the directive.
'Expected no space between opening parenthesis and directive in a declare statement'
// There should be no space between directive and the equal sign.
// The directive must be in lowercase.
'The directive of a declare statement must be in lowercase'
'Expected no space between directive and the equals sign in a declare statement'
// There should be no space between equal sign and directive value.
'Expected no space between equal sign and the directive value in a declare statement'
'Expected no space between the directive value and closing parenthesis in a declare statement'
'Expected no space between the closing parenthesis and the semicolon in a declare statement'
// Close tag must be on the same line..
'The close tag must be on the same line as the declare statement'
'Expected no space between the closing parenthesis and the semicolon in a declare statement'
// See if there is a semicolon or curly bracket after this token.
'Expected one space between closing parenthesis and opening curly bracket in a declare statement'
// The opening curly bracket must on the same line with a single space between closing bracket.

'The closing curly bracket of a declare statement must be on a new line'
// Closing curly bracket must align with the declare keyword.
'The closing curly bracket of a declare statements must be aligned with the declare keyword'
